lead_paragraph: Iceland survived a missed penalty as they began their bid to qualify for a first-ever World Cup by holding Ukraine to a 1-1 draw away from home on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Iceland Survive Missed Penalty and Hold Ukraine Away
